A Maelephant (MAY-luh-font) is a powerful guardian Fiend used to protect and defend the treasuries of Baatezu and wizards. They are humanoid in shape, standing 9 ft. tall and weighing 800 pounds. Their hands are oversized for their body, tipped with claws. Their heads are similar to a small-eared elephant's head. They willingly serve any who can provide enough flesh for them to devour. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    PS Monstrous Compendium I        
              
                    Fiend Folio (3ed)